      "acceptanceCriteria": "Version-controlled surrogate codebase with unit tests covering data pipeline, feature engineering, and inference path; documented training environment.",
      "rationale": "The gradient-boosted surrogate and its training pipeline are maintained under Git version control with tagged releases. Unit tests cover the ETL pipeline, feature-scaling transforms, and inference wrapper. A requirements.txt with pinned dependency versions is archived alongside the model artifact. SQA level 2 is satisfied."
    },
    {
