      "rationale": "The held-out test set covers all 5 flow-speed combinations specified in the COU (2–6 L/min, 2000–4000 RPM). Input boundary conditions (fluid viscosity, density, inlet pressure) are fixed at nominal values consistent with the CFD reference dataset. Conditions are entirely within the training distribution."
