      "rationale": "MAPE on the test set is 3.1%. Bland-Altman analysis yields mean bias of +0.011 RH units and 95% limits of agreement of [−0.063, +0.085], narrowly within the ±0.08 criterion. Agreement is assessed exclusively at nominal operating conditions; no comparison under perturbed or shifted inputs is provided."
    },
    {
