      "rationale": "Training and test data were generated by CFD simulation of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump geometry under CPB-representative boundary conditions. The validation activities are directly aligned with the COU device class, operating envelope, and fluid properties. Distribution-shift relevance (e.g., patient-to-patient haematocrit variability) is not addressed."
    },
